optional_parameters.name: filters_data
optional_parameters.description:
All available filters can be found under \"filter_groups\" field from response.
The \"filters_data\" value must be JSON array in format: [{simple filter button},{range/multiple select}, and more filters].

Example for {simple filter button} - {\"type\": 2, \"value\":\"true\"}.
Example for {range/multiple select} - {\"type\":8,\"value_list\": [\"1,1000\"]}.

Full example with filter by \"price\" and \"4 Stars & Up\": [{\"type\": 2, \"value\\\":\"true\"},{\"type\":8, \"value_list\": [\"1,1000\"]}]
